      "message": "To me, it appears this is the only thing main.go cares about, so let\u0027s make it the only exported struct (from this file) and call it Deployment (In kubernetes, instance+service is essentially the breakdown of all gold deployments)\n\nLet\u0027s add a new struct deploymentOptions with Internal/ConfigMap then a struct deploymentWithOptions that embeds both.",
